{"code":"","content":"<h3><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Comic Sans MS'\">【问题描述】</span></h3>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">火车从始发站（称为第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">站）开出，在始发站上车的人数为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">a</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">，然后到达第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">站，在第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">站有人上、下车，但上、下车的人数相同，因此在第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">站开出时（即在到达第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">站之前）车上的人数保持为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">a</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">人。从第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">站起（包括第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">站）上、下车的人数有一定规律：上车的人数都是前两站上车人数之和，而下车人数等于上一站上车人数，一直到终点站的前一站（第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">n-1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">站），都满足此规律。现给出的条件是：共有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">N</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">个车站，始发站上车的人数为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">a</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">，最后一站下车的人数是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">m</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">（全部下车）。试问</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">x</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">站开出时车上的人数是多少？</span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Comic Sans MS'\">【输入】</span></h3>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">输入</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">包含一行，</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">有四个正整数：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">a</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">a&lt;=100</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">），</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">n</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">n&lt;=20</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">），</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">m</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">m&lt;=10000</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">）和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">x</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">x&lt;=19</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">）</span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Comic Sans MS'\">【输出】</span></h3>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">输出</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">为一个整数，为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">x</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">站开出时车上的人数。</span></p>\n<p><br />\n&nbsp;</p>","fcontent":"<div class='pdsec'>问题描述</div><div class='pdcont'>　　火车从始发站（称为第1站）开出，在始发站上车的人数为a，然后到达第2站，在第2站有人上、下车，但上、下车的人数相同，因此在第2站开出时（即在到达第3站之前）车上的人数保持为a人。从第3站起（包括第3站）上、下车的人数有一定规律：上车的人数都是前两站上车人数之和，而下车人数等于上一站上车人数，一直到终点站的前一站（第n-1站），都满足此规律。现给出的条件是：共有N个车站，始发站上车的人数为a，最后一站下车的人数是m（全部下车）。试问x站开出时车上的人数是多少？</div><div class='pdsec'>输入格式</div><div class='pdcont'>　　输入包含一行， 有四个正整数：a（a&lt;=100），n（n&lt;=20），m（m&lt;=10000）和x（x&lt;=19）</div><div class='pdsec'>输出格式</div><div class='pdcont'>　　输出为一个整数，为x站开出时车上的人数。</div>\n","files":"","gpid":"A1117","indatacount":0,"inputfile":"","langs":"CPP,C0X,VC9,C,JAVA,PAS,PYTHON","memorylimit":"256.0MB","opid":0,"outputfile":"","remain":0,"ret":1,"specialjudge":"","src":"NOIP1998 提高组","subinter":0,"timelimit":"1.0s","title":"火车过站","type":"DEFAULT"}